rComments: Cutest prof I've ever had! Super sweet, Goodfair grader Lost my book for the final exam and she  took the time to scan every page we needed to read and send them to me personally by email.  Very nice prof and tries to get everyone to participate in debates and discussions
A great professorteacher.  She knows a lot and conveys it well.  Gives good feedback and likes to discuss the subject matter, which she obviously cares about.

Awesome professor.  Really nice and approachable, clear, and cares about your learning.  Brings in interesting examples and knows a lot about the subject matter.  Always prepared for class and made the subject enjoyable and interesting.  Thank you!
One of the best profs at OttawaU. Interesting classes and she puts a lot of effort into them.

Rating system makes no sense; vague outlines for assignments but looks for specificity. Boring slides and teaching style. She has lots of hands-on experience but overall lacking in keeping people engaged.
Really sweet, very interesting and also very helpful. She clearly loves teaching.
